NR4 = narrow range 4
NR7 = narrow range 7

effective on high beta stocks as they do not want to stay contracted, soon they rebel in up or dn direction

Narrow Range 4 and Narrow Range 7 help to find the calm so that we can prepare and profit from the impending storm.
Market goes through regular contraction and expansion cycle.

“The quiet period before the next explosive market move is like the calm before the storm”

In this trade setup, you should wait patiently for market
in order to enter in contraction which means for range of the bars to reduce.
Once we spot NR4 or NR7, a bigger price movement and direction is expected.
It is a breakout and reversal pattern which helps to generate profit after a range.

NR4 is the fourth day trading range is less than previous days and NR7 is the seventh day range is less than previous days.
NR4 and NR 7 scanners are available on chartink


